  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Digseum is a short, unique incremental journey about digging up ancient relics and building the greatest museum ever!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Excavate for ancient relics across the world</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361470/extras/0334b7cd9142763d904dc2828cb80526.poster.avif?t=1746551330\" width=600 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361470/extras/0334b7cd9142763d904dc2828cb80526.webm?t=1746551330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361470/extras/0334b7cd9142763d904dc2828cb80526.mp4?t=1746551330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage your resources and upgrade your abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361470/extras/3eada90ab328927cfb0026283c74f686.poster.avif?t=1746551330\" width=600 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361470/extras/3eada90ab328927cfb0026283c74f686.webm?t=1746551330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361470/extras/3eada90ab328927cfb0026283c74f686.mp4?t=1746551330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build the biggest and greatest museum the world has ever seen!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361470/extras/72fc54d8f8f4ff338779d2bc79f68b5d.poster.avif?t=1746551330\" width=600 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361470/extras/72fc54d8f8f4ff338779d2bc79f68b5d.webm?t=1746551330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361470/extras/72fc54d8f8f4ff338779d2bc79f68b5d.mp4?t=1746551330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dig up relics from a variety of locations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Display them in your museum to attract visitors</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Acquire money to upgrade your museum and excavation abilities</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relaxing incremental progression</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >12+ excavation sites</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50+ relics to discover</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skill tree of upgrades to explore</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Short and sweet experience (~2.5hr playtime)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chill lofi soundtrack, composed by Loyalty Freak Music</p></li></ul>",
